            <description><![CDATA[<style>body,*{font-family:-apple-system,system-ui;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5}h2{font-size:15px;margin:0 0 6px}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin:3px 0}code{background:rgba(127,127,127,.18);padding:1px 4px;border-radius:4px}</style><h2>Oxine 1.2.6</h2><ul><li><strong>Caffeine</strong>: a new footer control (the bolt) to keep your Mac awake. Left-click starts a timed session at your default duration; click again to stop.</li><li>Right-click the bolt to pick how long to stay awake. Your choice becomes the new default.</li><li>Live countdown shows in the footer while it runs; set the default duration in Settings.</li><li>Optional <strong>Keep apps active</strong>: nudges input when the system goes idle so Teams and Slack don&#x27;t flip to &quot;Away&quot; (needs Accessibility permission).</li></ul>]]></description>
